cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM 

This paper deals with face recognition, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed approach involves using deep neural networks (cs.LG) and generating synthetic images (cs.AI) to augment the training dataset. The paper also involves 3D shape estimation and rendering (cs.GR) and presents quantitative results on a challenging dataset (cs.MM).
